    <paragraph id="3.13.10.6.1.4" type="REQUIREMENT" scope="OBU">[2]; (The train has passed with its max safe front end the RSM start location if is calculatedfrom an EBD) OR (The train has passed with its estimated front end the RSM start location if it is calculated from the SBD); ;LEAVES TSM ; REACHES RSM</paragraph>
