    <paragraph id="6.5.1.2.14" type="REQUIREMENT" scope="OBU" >{CR719} Clause 3.12.3.4.3.2 shall not apply.</paragraph>
    <paragraph id="6.5.1.2.15" type="REQUIREMENT" scope="OBU">{CR763} Clauses 3.12.3.1.11 and 3.12.3.5.1 shall not apply.</paragraph>
    <paragraph id="6.5.1.2.16" type="REQUIREMENT" scope="OBU">{CR637} Clause 3.12.4.1 shall be replaced with: “The Mode Profile can request On Sight mode and Shunting mode.”</paragraph>
    <paragraph id="6.5.1.2.17" type="REQUIREMENT" scope="OBU">{CR637} Clause 3.12.4.2 shall be replaced with: “For OS mode the mode profile shall define the entry and the length of the On Sight area. For SH mode the mode profile only defines the entry location to SH mode, any length given shall be ignored by the on-board.”</paragraph>
    <paragraph id="6.5.1.2.18" type="REQUIREMENT" scope="OBU" >{CR745} Clause 3.15.1.2.3.1 p) shall not apply.</paragraph>
    <paragraph id="6.5.1.2.19" type="REQUIREMENT" scope="OBU" >{CR756} Clause 3.15.9.2 shall not apply.</paragraph>
